> I think having Nikhil's review on this is important.

Ian's gone now :) just keep that in mind. He won't be iterating on this any further. Someone else will probably need to take ownership here.
Or, we pass it, and we add to it later.

Patch Set 4:

I'll ping both Nikhil and Flavio to take a quick look.  The key thing right now is that Ian's successor, Hemanth, has read what's in here, so we don't need to rush to publish.  However, as Alexandra points out, if we are going to iterate on it, someone will have to take it over.  I guess I can do that.
